trans-unit.source: Copies the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> objects from this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> into the specified array, starting at the specified position index in array.
trans-unit.target: 从数组中指定的位置索引开始，将 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> 对象从此 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> 复制到指定的数组中。

trans-unit.target: `array` 必须是一维数组。

trans-unit.source: If it is not, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 如果不是，<xref:System.ArgumentException>引发。

trans-unit.source: Further exceptions are thrown if the number of elements to copy is greater than the available space from `index` to the end of `array`, if `array` is `null`, or if `index` is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: 如果要复制的元素数大于从的可用空间，则引发进一步异常`index`到末尾`array`，如果`array`是`null`，或者如果`index`小于 0。

trans-unit.source: However, it is possible that another API created the duplicate.

trans-unit.source: Copies the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> objects from this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> into the specified array, starting at the specified position index in array.
trans-unit.target: 从数组中指定的位置索引开始，将 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> 对象从此 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> 复制到指定的数组中。

trans-unit.source: `array` must be one-dimensional.
trans-unit.target: `array` 必须是一维数组。

trans-unit.source: If it is not, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 如果不是，<xref:System.ArgumentException>引发。

trans-unit.source: Further exceptions are thrown if the number of elements to copy is greater than the available space from `index` to the end of `array`, if `array` is `null`, or if `index` is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: 如果要复制的元素数大于从的可用空间，则引发进一步异常`index`到末尾`array`，如果`array`是`null`，或者如果`index`小于 0。

trans-unit.target: 返回一个枚举数，用于循环访问 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> 中的主体。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> containing the principals in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />，包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> 中的主体。

trans-unit.target: 尽管多次调用<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.System%23Collections%23IEnumerable%23GetEnumerator%2A>返回不同<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>对象，它们共享相同的内部状态。
